name: Mango Overrides Token List
description: This file contains token details for specific tokens where we can't use the main SPL token registry. This is often the result of the SPL token registry changing symbols (e.g. ETH -> soETH) which will confuse lookups.

symbol-change.name: symbol-change
symbol-change.description: Tokens that have a different symbol in the main SPL token registry

stablecoin.name: stablecoin
stablecoin.description: Tokens that are fixed to an external asset, e.g. the US dollar
